  "topics": {
    "topic_world": {
      "id": "topic_world",
      "name": "Ashvale Compact",
      "type": "topic",
      "parentId": null,
      "content": "<p><strong style=\"font-size:20px;\">Ashvale Compact • MTG Topic Frame</strong></p><p>\n</p><p><em>3-column layout: linked entities, core lore, and related quick-notes.</em></p><p>\n</p><p><img data-lore-image=\"topic-world\" src=\"assets/world_builder.png\" alt=\"Ashvale Compact skyline\" style=\"display: block; margin: 8px auto 14px; max-width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); border-radius: 4px; position: relative; cursor: default; touch-action: none; pointer-events: auto;\" data-resizable=\"true\" class=\"img-resize-enabled\" draggable=\"false\"></p><table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; table-layout: fixed; width: 100%; border: 2px solid rgb(200, 162, 74); background: rgb(26, 29, 34);\" data-clear-border=\"1\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td contenteditable=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"textbox\" style=\"width: 23%; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); background: rgb(34, 40, 49); padding: 10px;\" class=\"table-cell-multi-selected\" data-clear-border=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n        </span><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">Linked Items</span></h3><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n        </span><p style=\"margin:6px 0 4px 0;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">Topics</strong></p><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n        </span><ul><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_magic\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" style=\"color: rgb(226, 230, 0);\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Ember Weave</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 230, 0);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_accord\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" style=\"color: rgb(226, 230, 0);\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Lantern Accord</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 230, 0);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_sunder\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" style=\"color: rgb(226, 230, 0);\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Sundered Kilns</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 230, 0);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_choir\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" style=\"color: rgb(226, 230, 0);\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Ash Choir</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 230, 0);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_furnace\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" style=\"color: rgb(226, 230, 0);\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Furnace Oath</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n        </span></ul><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n        </span><p style=\"margin:8px 0 4px 0;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">Characters</strong></p><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n        </span><ul><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/character/char_lyra\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-character\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 178, 39);\" data-item-link-type=\"character\">Lyra Voss</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 178, 39);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/character/char_bram\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-character\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 178, 39);\" data-item-link-type=\"character\">Bram Kest</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 178, 39);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/character/char_sable\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-character\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 178, 39);\" data-item-link-type=\"character\">Sable Mire</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(36, 178, 39);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/character/char_oren\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-character\" style=\"color: rgb(36, 178, 39);\" data-item-link-type=\"character\">Oren Pike</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n        </span></ul><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n        </span><p style=\"margin:8px 0 4px 0;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">Timeline</strong></p><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n        </span><ul><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/event/event_black_dawn\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-event\" style=\"color: rgb(240, 128, 0);\" data-item-link-type=\"event\">The Black Dawn Breach</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(240, 128, 0);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/event/event_cinderfall\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-event\" style=\"color: rgb(240, 128, 0);\" data-item-link-type=\"event\">Cinderfall Convocation</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n        </span></ul><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n        </span><p style=\"margin:8px 0 4px 0;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">Markers</strong></p><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n        </span><ul><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/marker/marker_archive\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-marker\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 200, 240);\" data-item-link-type=\"marker\">Archive Vault Delta</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 200, 240);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/marker/marker_kilnheart\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-marker\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 200, 240);\" data-item-link-type=\"marker\">Kilnheart Mouth</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 200, 240);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/marker/marker_blackbell\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-marker\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 200, 240);\" data-item-link-type=\"marker\">Blackbell Relay</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 200, 240);\">\n          </span><li><a href=\"extal://item/marker/marker_quillfire\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-marker\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 200, 240);\" data-item-link-type=\"marker\">Quillfire Lab</a></li><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n        </span></ul><span style=\"color: rgb(243, 243, 236);\">\n      </span></td>\n      <td contenteditable=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"textbox\" style=\"width: 54%; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); background: rgb(31, 36, 43); padding: 12px;\" class=\"\" data-clear-border=\"1\">\n        <h1 style=\"margin-top:0;color:#f5e7b2;\">Ashvale Compact</h1>\n    <span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">    </span><p><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">The Ashvale Compact is a treaty-city raised over a dormant volcanic rift. Lantern roads connect archive districts, relay towers, and kiln wards while guild law keeps trade alive through ash-storm season.</span></p><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">\n        </span><p><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">Its civic doctrine is card-like in structure: <strong>Resource</strong> (open roads), <strong>Control</strong> (stable wards), and <strong>Tempo</strong> (relay timing). When any pillar fails, the city shifts from governance to survival mode.</span></p><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">\n        </span><h2><span style=\"color: rgb(254, 251, 154);\">Current Story State</span></h2><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">\n        </span><p><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">After the Black Dawn breach, Lyra and Bram stabilized command lines. One year later, the Cinderfall Convocation renewed the Furnace Oath and reopened sealed kiln annexes under strict supervision by Sable and Oren.</span></p><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">\n        </span><h2><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 251, 143);\">Operational Hooks</span></h2><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">\n        </span><ul><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">\n          </span><li><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">The Sundered Kilns produce memory-echo anomalies that can falsify route logs.</span></li><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">\n          </span><li><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">Ash Choir protocols now include a pre-tone for surge warnings.</span></li><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">\n          </span><li><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">Westwatch remains the highest-priority fallback command platform.</span></li><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">\n        </span></ul><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">\n        </span><p><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\"><strong>Map Focus:</strong> Embermarch Corridor (Exodus map file) with mixed placed and unplaced markers for active and planned play arcs.</span></p><span style=\"color: rgb(241, 237, 233);\">\n      </span></td>\n      <td contenteditable=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"textbox\" style=\"width: 23%; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); background: rgb(34, 40, 49); padding: 10px;\" class=\"\" data-clear-border=\"1\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\">\n        </span><h3 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 8px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\">Related Elements</span></h3><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\">\n        </span><p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\"><strong>Lyra Voss:</strong> Warden-scribe who sealed the first breach by hand; anchor for archive continuity.</span></p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\">\n        </span><p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\"><strong>Bram Kest:</strong> Route captain who keeps civilian corridors open under convoy pressure.</span></p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\">\n        </span><p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\"><strong>Sable Mire:</strong> Kiln alchemist measuring vent chemistry and instability drift.</span></p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\">\n        </span><p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\"><strong>Oren Pike:</strong> Relay marshal maintaining cross-district signal integrity.</span></p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\">\n        </span><p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\"><strong>Black Dawn:</strong> Disaster event that forced emergency law revisions.</span></p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\">\n        </span><p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\"><strong>Cinderfall:</strong> Treaty renewal that formalized new succession rules.</span></p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\">\n        </span><p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\"><strong>Kilnheart Mouth:</strong> Active fracture vent tied to recent pressure surges.</span></p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\">\n        </span><p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\"><strong>Blackbell Relay:</strong> Tower used for silence windows during high council sessions.</span></p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\">\n        </span><p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\"><strong>Template Note:</strong> Reuse this frame for other Topics by swapping center article text and updating left/right references.</span></p><span style=\"color: rgb(237, 237, 232);\">\n      </span></td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table><p><span style=\"color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"><span class=\"\">﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿﻿</span></span>\n</p><p><br></p><p>\n</p>",
