    "topic_sunder": {
      "id": "topic_sunder",
      "name": "Sundered Kilns",
      "type": "topic",
      "parentId": "topic_world",
      "content": "<p><strong style=\"font-size:20px;\">Ashvale Compact • MTG Topic Frame</strong></p><p>\n</p><p><em>Topic Card: Sundered Kilns</em></p><p>\n</p><p><img data-lore-image=\"topic-sunder\" src=\"assets/old_city.webp\" alt=\"Sundered Kilns district ruins\" style=\"display: block; margin: 8px auto 14px; max-width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); border-radius: 4px; position: relative; cursor: default; touch-action: none; pointer-events: auto;\" data-resizable=\"true\" class=\"img-resize-enabled\" draggable=\"false\"></p><table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;table-layout:fixed;width:100%;border:2px solid #c8a24a;background:#1a1d22;\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td contenteditable=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"textbox\" style=\"width: 23%; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); background: rgb(34, 40, 49); padding: 10px;\" class=\"\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;color:#f0d78a;\">Linked Items</h3>\n        <p style=\"margin:6px 0 4px 0;\"><strong>Topics</strong></p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_world\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Ashvale Compact</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_choir\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Ash Choir</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_furnace\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Furnace Oath</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <p style=\"margin:8px 0 4px 0;\"><strong>Characters</strong></p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/character/char_sable\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-character\" data-item-link-type=\"character\">Sable Mire</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/character/char_oren\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-character\" data-item-link-type=\"character\">Oren Pike</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/character/char_lyra\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-character\" data-item-link-type=\"character\">Lyra Voss</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <p style=\"margin:8px 0 4px 0;\"><strong>Timeline</strong></p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/event/event_black_dawn\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-event\" data-item-link-type=\"event\">The Black Dawn Breach</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/event/event_cinderfall\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-event\" data-item-link-type=\"event\">Cinderfall Convocation</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <p style=\"margin:8px 0 4px 0;\"><strong>Marker</strong></p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/marker/marker_kilnheart\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-marker\" data-item-link-type=\"marker\">Kilnheart Mouth</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </td>\n      <td contenteditable=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"textbox\" style=\"width: 54%; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); background: rgb(31, 36, 43); padding: 12px;\" class=\"\">\n        <h1 style=\"margin-top:0;color:#f5e7b2;\">Sundered Kilns</h1>\n        <p>The Sundered Kilns are fractured industrial heat-vaults beneath Westwatch. Their unstable vents now emit blue resonance pulses that disrupt maps, memory, and relay timing.</p>\n        <h2>Threat Profile</h2>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Pressure surges can trigger chain faults across sealed routes.</li>\n          <li>Memory-echo effects create contradictory witness logs.</li>\n          <li>Kiln tremors can desync Ash Choir warning cadence.</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h2>Current Relevance</h2>\n        <p>Post-Cinderfall protocols opened select annexes for controlled study. Sable leads assay runs while Oren times relay quiet periods for safer measurements.</p>\n      </td>\n      <td contenteditable=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"textbox\" style=\"width: 23%; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); background: rgb(34, 40, 49); padding: 10px;\" class=\"\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;color:#f0d78a;\">Related Elements</h3>\n        <p><strong>Kilnheart Mouth:</strong> Main fracture vent and highest risk point.</p>\n        <p><strong>Sable:</strong> Primary kiln chemist and risk recorder.</p>\n        <p><strong>Oren:</strong> Maintains signal windows for safe vent work.</p>\n        <p><strong>Lyra:</strong> Validates breach-seal authority in field.</p>\n        <p><strong>Furnace Oath:</strong> Legal basis for emergency kiln command.</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table><p>\n</p><p><br></p><p>\n</p>",
      "editorBackground": "#3a2520",
      "order": 2,
      "links": {
