    "topic_choir": {
      "id": "topic_choir",
      "name": "Ash Choir",
      "type": "topic",
      "parentId": "topic_world",
      "content": "<p><strong style=\"font-size:20px;\">Ashvale Compact • MTG Topic Frame</strong></p><p>\n</p><p><em>Topic Card: Ash Choir</em></p><p>\n</p><p><img data-lore-image=\"topic-choir\" src=\"assets/crystal-758818_1280.webp\" alt=\"Ash Choir resonance crystal\" style=\"display: block; margin: 8px auto 14px; max-width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); border-radius: 4px; position: relative; cursor: default; touch-action: none; pointer-events: auto;\" data-resizable=\"true\" class=\"img-resize-enabled\" draggable=\"false\"></p><table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; table-layout: fixed; width: 100%; border: 2px solid rgb(200, 162, 74); background: rgb(26, 29, 34);\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td contenteditable=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"textbox\" style=\"width: 23%; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); background: rgb(34, 40, 49); padding: 10px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;color:#f0d78a;\">Linked Items</h3>\n        <p style=\"margin:6px 0 4px 0;\"><strong>Topics</strong></p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_world\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Ashvale Compact</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_sunder\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Sundered Kilns</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_furnace\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Furnace Oath</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <p style=\"margin:8px 0 4px 0;\"><strong>Characters</strong></p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/character/char_bram\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-character\" data-item-link-type=\"character\">Bram Kest</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/character/char_sable\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-character\" data-item-link-type=\"character\">Sable Mire</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/character/char_oren\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-character\" data-item-link-type=\"character\">Oren Pike</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <p style=\"margin:8px 0 4px 0;\"><strong>Timeline</strong></p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/event/event_black_dawn\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-event\" data-item-link-type=\"event\">The Black Dawn Breach</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/event/event_cinderfall\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-event\" data-item-link-type=\"event\">Cinderfall Convocation</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <p style=\"margin:8px 0 4px 0;\"><strong>Marker</strong></p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/marker/marker_blackbell\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-marker\" data-item-link-type=\"marker\">Blackbell Relay</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </td>\n      <td contenteditable=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"textbox\" style=\"width: 54%; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); background: rgb(31, 36, 43); padding: 12px;\">\n        <h1 style=\"margin-top:0;color:#f5e7b2;\">Ash Choir</h1>\n        <p>Ash Choir is a layered warning-cant transmitted by bell, horn, and tuned pipe along ember roads. It turns route status into timed signal stacks that can cut through dust blackout conditions.</p>\n        <h2>Signal Structure</h2>\n        <ul>\n          <li><strong>Pulse 1:</strong> route availability.</li>\n          <li><strong>Pulse 2:</strong> hazard class and spread direction.</li>\n          <li><strong>Pulse 3:</strong> command authority currently in force.</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h2>Current Relevance</h2>\n        <p>After kiln surge incidents, Oren introduced a new pre-tone tied to Sable's vent threshold tables. This lets Bram shift convoys before visible fault propagation.</p>\n      </td>\n      <td contenteditable=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"textbox\" style=\"width: 23%; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); background: rgb(34, 40, 49); padding: 10px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;color:#f0d78a;\">Related Elements</h3>\n        <p><strong>Blackbell Relay:</strong> Primary tower for high-tier Ash Choir broadcasts.</p>\n        <p><strong>Oren:</strong> Architect of current cadence tables.</p>\n        <p><strong>Sable:</strong> Provides hazard thresholds for pre-tone triggers.</p>\n        <p><strong>Bram:</strong> Converts signal calls into route movement orders.</p>\n        <p><strong>Cinderfall:</strong> Meeting where updated cant was ratified.</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table><p>\n</p><p><br></p><p>\n</p>",
      "editorBackground": "#2a2438",
      "order": 3,
      "links": {
