    "topic_furnace": {
      "id": "topic_furnace",
      "name": "Furnace Oath",
      "type": "topic",
      "parentId": "topic_world",
      "content": "<p><strong style=\"font-size:20px;\">Ashvale Compact • MTG Topic Frame</strong></p><p>\n</p><p><em>Topic Card: Furnace Oath</em></p><p>\n</p><p><img data-lore-image=\"topic-furnace\" src=\"assets/evil_eye_desc1.webp\" alt=\"Furnace Oath ward sigil\" style=\"display: block; margin: 8px auto 14px; max-width: 100%; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); border-radius: 4px; position: relative; cursor: default; touch-action: none; pointer-events: auto;\" data-resizable=\"true\" class=\"img-resize-enabled img-selected\" draggable=\"false\"></p><table style=\"border-collapse:collapse;table-layout:fixed;width:100%;border:2px solid #c8a24a;background:#1a1d22;\">\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td contenteditable=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"textbox\" style=\"width: 23%; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); background: rgb(34, 40, 49); padding: 10px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;color:#f0d78a;\">Linked Items</h3>\n        <p style=\"margin:6px 0 4px 0;\"><strong>Topics</strong></p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_world\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Ashvale Compact</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_accord\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Lantern Accord</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_sunder\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Sundered Kilns</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/topic/topic_choir\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-topic\" data-item-link-type=\"topic\">Ash Choir</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <p style=\"margin:8px 0 4px 0;\"><strong>Characters</strong></p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/character/char_lyra\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-character\" data-item-link-type=\"character\">Lyra Voss</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/character/char_bram\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-character\" data-item-link-type=\"character\">Bram Kest</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/character/char_sable\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-character\" data-item-link-type=\"character\">Sable Mire</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/character/char_oren\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-character\" data-item-link-type=\"character\">Oren Pike</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <p style=\"margin:8px 0 4px 0;\"><strong>Timeline</strong></p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/event/event_black_dawn\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-event\" data-item-link-type=\"event\">The Black Dawn Breach</a></li>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/event/event_cinderfall\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-event\" data-item-link-type=\"event\">Cinderfall Convocation</a></li>\n        </ul>\n        <p style=\"margin:8px 0 4px 0;\"><strong>Marker</strong></p>\n        <ul>\n          <li><a href=\"extal://item/marker/marker_westwatch\" class=\"extal-item-link extal-item-link-marker\" data-item-link-type=\"marker\">Westwatch Platform</a></li>\n        </ul>\n      </td>\n      <td contenteditable=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"textbox\" style=\"width: 54%; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); background: rgb(31, 36, 43); padding: 12px;\">\n        <h1 style=\"margin-top:0;color:#f5e7b2;\">Furnace Oath</h1>\n        <p>The Furnace Oath is the Compact's crisis-override doctrine. In breach conditions, command transfers to the first qualified stabilizer, then descends by predeclared succession if relays collapse.</p>\n        <h2>Activation Conditions</h2>\n        <ul>\n          <li>Confirmed pressure fault with route impact risk.</li>\n          <li>Relay degradation across two or more sectors.</li>\n          <li>Archive witness and signal record attached within one cycle.</li>\n        </ul>\n        <h2>Current Relevance</h2>\n        <p>Cinderfall renewed the Oath with explicit handoff language, reducing command delay during multi-site faults and preserving legal continuity under Lantern Accord review.</p>\n      </td>\n      <td contenteditable=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"textbox\" style=\"width: 23%; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid rgb(109, 85, 48); background: rgb(34, 40, 49); padding: 10px;\">\n        <h3 style=\"margin:0 0 8px 0;color:#f0d78a;\">Related Elements</h3>\n        <p><strong>Westwatch Platform:</strong> Default Oath command staging point.</p>\n        <p><strong>Lantern Accord:</strong> Parent legal framework for Oath usage.</p>\n        <p><strong>Black Dawn:</strong> Event that exposed old succession gaps.</p>\n        <p><strong>Cinderfall:</strong> Event that codified corrected handoff order.</p>\n        <p><strong>All Four Wardens:</strong> Current practical executors of Oath protocols.</p>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table><p>\n</p><p><br></p><p>\n</p>",
      "editorBackground": "#2f2a1b",
