  "events": {
    "event_black_dawn": {
      "id": "event_black_dawn",
      "name": "The Black Dawn Breach",
      "type": "event",
      "date": "Year 312, Embermonth 03",
      "endDate": "Year 312, Embermonth 04",
      "category": "Disaster Response",
      "description": "<h2>The Black Dawn Breach</h2><p>Before sunrise, a pressure fault opened beneath the southern lantern line. Lyra sealed the inner channel while Bram led evac convoys through ashfall crosswinds.</p><p>The breach was contained, but one district was abandoned and the Accord emergency clauses were permanently revised.</p>",
      "content": "<h2>The Black Dawn Breach</h2><p>Before sunrise, a pressure fault opened beneath the southern lantern line. Lyra sealed the inner channel while Bram led evac convoys through ashfall crosswinds.</p><p>The breach was contained, but one district was abandoned and the Accord emergency clauses were permanently revised.</p>",
      "links": {
        "characters": [
          "char_bram",
          "char_lyra",
          "char_oren",
          "char_sable"
        ],
        "topics": [
