    "event_cinderfall": {
      "id": "event_cinderfall",
      "name": "Cinderfall Convocation",
      "type": "event",
      "date": "Year 313, Embermonth 01",
      "endDate": "Year 313, Embermonth 01",
      "category": "Treaty Renewal",
      "description": "<h2>Cinderfall Convocation</h2><p>Guild delegates convened at Westwatch to renew the Furnace Oath after kiln tremors resurfaced. Sable presented vent data while Oren coordinated signal silence windows for secure deliberation.</p><p>The Convocation ratified new emergency command succession and opened sealed kiln annexes for controlled study.</p>",
      "content": "<h2>Cinderfall Convocation</h2><p>Guild delegates convened at Westwatch to renew the Furnace Oath after kiln tremors resurfaced. Sable presented vent data while Oren coordinated signal silence windows for secure deliberation.</p><p>The Convocation ratified new emergency command succession and opened sealed kiln annexes for controlled study.</p>",
      "links": {
